Package com.google.code.beanmatchers

Interface ValueGenerator<T>

Type Parameters:
T - The type of value produced.
public interface ValueGenerator<T>
Generates instances of a specific type.

  • Method Summary

    Modifier and Type Method Description
    T generate()
    Generate a new instance.

  • Method Details

    • generate

      T generate()
      Generate a new instance. The new should have random value. Specifically, two sequential calls to this method should result (with high probability, not guaranteed) in two distinct values - values that are not equal as per their equals() method.
      Returns:
      A new instance of random value.
